query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS coverage_cells (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  year INT NOT NULL,
  sector VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
  governorate VARCHAR(100),
  actorType VARCHAR(100),
  regimeTag ENUM('aden_irg','sanaa_defacto','mixed','unknown'),
  totalExpectedItems INT DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  totalAvailableItems INT DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  coverageScore DECIMAL(5,2),
  indicatorsCovered INT DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  indicatorsExpected INT DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  eventsCovered INT DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  eventsExpected INT DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  documentsCovered INT DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  documentsExpected INT DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  regulationsCovered INT DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  regulationsExpected INT DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  averageConfidence DECIMAL(3,2),
  lastUpdatedAt TIMESTAMP NULL,
  createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  updatedAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  INDEX coverage_year_idx (year),
  INDEX coverage_sector_idx (sector),
  INDEX coverage_gov_idx (governorate),
  INDEX coverage_regime_idx (regimeTag),
  INDEX coverage_score_idx (coverageScore)
);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS coverage_items (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  cellId INT NOT NULL,
  itemType ENUM('indicator','event','document','regulation','actor','page') NOT NULL,
  itemId VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
  itemLabel VARCHAR(255),
  status ENUM('available','missing','partial','outdated') NOT NULL,
  lastAvailableDate TIMESTAMP NULL,
  confidenceGrade ENUM('A','B','C','D'),
  dataGapTicketId INT,
  createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  updatedAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  INDEX coverage_item_cell_idx (cellId),
  INDEX coverage_item_type_idx (itemType),
  INDEX coverage_item_status_idx (status),
  FOREIGN KEY (cellId) REFERENCES coverage_cells(id)
);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS fix_tickets (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  ticketType ENUM('hardcoded_value','broken_link','missing_provenance','export_failure','translation_missing','ui_inconsistency','performance_issue','security_issue','other') NOT NULL,
  filePath VARCHAR(500),
  lineNumber INT,
  pageRoute VARCHAR(255),
  componentName VARCHAR(100),
  title VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  description TEXT NOT NULL,
  detectedValue TEXT,
  expectedBehavior TEXT,
  severity ENUM('low','medium','high','critical') DEFAULT 'medium' NOT NULL,
  status ENUM('open','in_progress','resolved','wont_fix','duplicate') DEFAULT 'open' NOT NULL,
  resolvedByUserId INT,
  resolvedAt TIMESTAMP NULL,
  resolutionNotes TEXT,
  detectedByJobId INT,
  detectedAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  updatedAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  INDEX fix_ticket_type_idx (ticketType),
  INDEX fix_ticket_severity_idx (severity),
  INDEX fix_ticket_status_idx (status),
  INDEX fix_ticket_page_idx (pageRoute)
);
